		<span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">﻿﻿ </span>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: x-large;"><strong><span style="color: #000000;">《月上弦梢》元宵节音乐会</span></strong></span></p>
<p style="text-align: center; padding-left: 30px;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">时间：<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">2013</span>年<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">2</span>月<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">24</span>日                  </span></p>
<p style="text-align: center; padding-left: 30px;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">地点：国家大剧院音乐厅            </span></p>
<p style="text-align: center; padding-left: 30px;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">指挥：许知俊（国家一级指挥）</span></p>
<p style="text-align: center; padding-left: 30px;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">首席：唐峰（国家一级演员）     </span></p>
<p style="text-align: center; padding-left: 30px;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">主持人：耿靓 <span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">                               </span></span></p>
 
<p><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;"> </span></p>
<p><span style="color: #000000; font-size: small;">一、民族管弦乐《节日序曲》<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">                                                                                                         </span>施万春曲<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;"> </span>张列改编<br /></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="color: #000000;">二、</span><span style="color: #000000;">民族管弦乐《欢乐歌》<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">                                                                                                         </span>江南丝竹<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;"> </span>王甫建改编</span></span></p>
<p><span style="color: #000000; font-size: small;">三、琵琶独奏《春雨》<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">                                                                                                                                   </span>朱毅<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;"> </span>文博曲</span></p>
<p>
<p><span style="color: #000000; font-size: small;">                                                   琵琶演奏：赵聪</span></p>
</p>
<p><span style="color: #000000; font-size: small;">       （国家一级演员、<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">”</span>天华杯<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">”</span>全国专业琵琶大赛金奖、文化部优秀剧目展演优秀奖获奖者）</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #000000; font-size: small;">四、二胡、笛子与乐队《凤凰魅影》<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">                      </span>根据电视剧《甄嬛传》插曲改编创作<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">  </span>刘欢曲<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;"> </span>赵东升改编</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #000000; font-size: small;">           二胡演奏：段超（金钟奖获奖者）<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">        </span>笛子演奏：丁晓奎（<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">CCTV</span>民族乐器大赛获奖者）</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #000000; font-size: small;">五、民族管弦乐《丝绸之路》<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">                                                                                                                                  </span>姜莹曲</span></p>
<p>
<p><span style="font-family: Times New Roman; color: #000000; font-size: small;"> </span></p>
