<p><span style="color: #000000; font-size: small;">六、民族管弦乐《闹春》                                                                                    <span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">                           </span>朱彬曲</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #000000; font-size: small;">七、二胡与乐队《二泉映月》<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">                                                                                                        </span>华彦钧曲<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;"> </span>王祖皆编曲</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #000000; font-size: small;">            二胡演奏：李源源（国家一级演员、文化部优秀剧目展演优秀奖获奖者、金钟奖获奖者）</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #000000; font-size: small;">八、笛子独奏《喜相逢》<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">                                                                                                                 </span>民间乐曲<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;"> </span>冯子存编曲</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #000000; font-size: small;">                   笛子演奏：王次恒（国家一级演员、文化部优秀剧目展演优秀奖获奖者）</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #000000; font-size: small;">九、民族管弦乐《关东情》<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">                                                                                                                                     </span>隋利军曲</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #000000; font-size: small;">十、二胡齐奏《赛马》<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">                                                                                                                       </span>黄海怀曲<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;"> </span>陈思昂编配</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #000000; font-size: small;">                                       二胡演奏：李源源、詹丽君等</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #000000; font-size: small;">十一、民族管弦乐《火车托卡塔》<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">                                                                                                         </span>刘湲曲<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;"> </span>姜莹改编</span></p>
